{"word":"H7050 - קֶלַע - qelaʻ - keh'-lah - Hanging","slug":"H7050","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קֶלַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qelaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>keh'-lah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hanging"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05DC;&#x05E2; - qela&#x201B;</b> - <i>kah'-lah</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7049\">H7049</a>; a <i>sling</i>; also a (door) <i>screen</i> (as if <i>slung</i> across), or the <i>valve</i> (of the door) itself: - hanging, leaf, sling."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7049\">H7049</a>, <a href=\"#/H7051\">H7051</a>"}]}